data.description: Amazing Alpine home on 4 acre plot of land with great VIEWS! Enjoy the beauty of a extremely private gated home that has a 300 degree view of the surrounding area. This 4 acre property is zoned A70 and is ready for any homesteading or agricultural goals with already build horse pen built on the property. This 1440 sq foot home has 2 bed/ 2 bath with an additional converted movie room in the garage that can easily be used as a third room (the movie room is not counted towards the current sqft). The master suite is equip with large walk-in closet. From this property you have quick access to the highway and can be in downtown San Diego in only 30 minutes! This is a MUST SEE property. No HOA, no Mello-Roos.
